description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if in the NFL Season Opener between the Kansas City Chiefs and the Baltimore Ravens scheduled for September 5, 8:20 PM ET the following occurs; 

- Travis Kelce scores a touchdown (including passing)
- The Kansas City Chiefs win the game
- Taylor Swift is shown live in the stadium on the NBC TV Broadcast at least once during the game between the opening kickoff and the completion of the final play of the game. 

Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If the game is not completed by September 12, 2024 (11:59 PM ET) the market will resolve to “No”.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from the NFL and live footage from NBC’s broadcast of the game, however a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
